channel.description:
[CENTER][IMG]http://pr-forum.net/images/MyRed/logo.png[/img]
Download client: [url=https://www.dropbox.com/s/gcoktqv8pm9q780/Project%20Raw%20Client.jar?dl=0]https://www.dropbox.com/s/gcoktqv8pm9q780/Project%20Raw%20Client.jar?dl=0[/url]
Website: [url=http://pr-forum.net/]http://pr-forum.net/[/url]
Project Raw is a brand new server that has just been released again and we're rapidly growing with lots of great features and loads of content. We're currently looking for some experienced staff members that are mature and capable for the spot! (no staffhunters). Project Raw is PKing, Skilling and PVMing based server or actually its a server for everyone, who likes skilling, pking, pvming and stuff like that! Our current players are friendly to everyone, so that's why the community is good atm. It's more fun to play a server with great community. Friendly and funny players make the game more enjoyable. Project Raw is not the server which has the best features, but the community makes the game better! We are offering a lot of things. Tons of bosses to kill, working every skill and some challenging minigames!
Also we are 24/7 open. Website is up, but the vote system, highscores and webclient will be on as soon as possible! Server has a has no ecomony yet, since it's fresh and young, and there's no spawning and any items people obtain will have been earned through PVM, Skilling, PKing, Voting or Donating. About the money making in server is pretty easy. You start with stalls, (like always). You can PvM alone or with friends, and share the drops! At the moment with low player count, PvM'ing is probably the best money making!
Why not come and test the server out?
I am currently looking for experienced Web Developer as well! Since our website isn't the best one, but should be good enough. Hit me up, if you are interested so we can discuss about Website's through Skype.
[IMG]http://209.190.33.194/images/04b/04b221f11f31f637797b9ea7142a20497b40ac28.png[/img]
-24/7 Online -Daily Updates -OSRS Items -Switchable gameframe -Achievements -Tons of bosses to kill -FunPK -Properly working Clan Chat -Minigames -Perfect Switching -PKP system + killstreaks -Active forums -Mature and experienced staff team -Lottery System -All working skills -Completionist cape -Prestige 5 levels -Slayer System (You can choose your task level) -Double Experience every weekend -All Working 20 skills! -Perfect switching and pvp -Completionist cape -Nothing is too hard or too easy -Active owner and staff team -Godwars -Custom titles
And much much more!
